b) MULTI-CORE DECODING - MX Player is the first Android video player which supports multi-core decoding. Test result proved that dual-core deviceâ€™s performance is up to 70% better than single-core devices. 

c) PINCH TO ZOOM, ZOOM AND PAN - Easily zoom in and out by pinching and swiping across the screen. Zoom and Pan is also available by option. 

d) SUBTITLE GESTURES - Scroll forward/backward to move to next
